author: MandaloreGaming
description:
Legendary, also known as Legendary The Box, is a mythical themed FPS where New York is attacked by fire drakes, griffins, and golems after an uninformed thief opens Pandora's Box in an art museum unleashing animus energy. There are two feuding illuminatis and lots of werewolves. The MrLetsPlayNintendo classic returns!
